{"tid":2411953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸民眾續上街抗議　據報周三示威規模屬政變以來最大","createTime":"2021-02-17T16:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T04:15:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cc81b3e5ae3d42852d91422014e7956890cd4377","tid":2411953,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576110-20210218.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576110-20210218.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=0d7700de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576110-20210218.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=815fda27\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576110-20210218.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸民眾繼續上街，抗議軍方發動政變。美聯社說，星期三的示威規模是政變以來最大。有監察團體說，自政變以來，已經有450多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n在最大城市仰光， 大批示威者堵塞市中心的馬路，有人將汽車停在路上，限制軍車和警車流動。有參與抗議的學生說，會展現團結力量，去結束軍事統治，強調會戰鬥到底。<br />\n<br />\n首都內比都有來自不同行業的民眾遊行，幾十人就為上星期被橡膠子彈擊中、目前情況危殆的年輕女子舉行禱告會。<br />\n<br />\n軍方表示，一名警員星期日在第二大城市曼德勒與示威者衝突期間殉職，強調會對違法的人採取行動。軍方又向多位著名演員、導演和歌手發出拘捕令，指控他們利用人氣和名望，去煽動民眾參加反對軍方的公民抗命運動。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國緬甸人權問題特別報告員安德魯斯警告，軍方調派士兵到仰光，可能導致局勢急速失控。"},{"pid":"f2be40b02330049d4eb369a927d2fb4d5772c5fa","tid":2411953,"uid":13221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"星期三唔洗返工咩"},{"pid":"658c5d824d6ae94489fe97bcc445b69442222fa9","tid":2411953,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"六千萬人口既國家<br />\n出黎既人仲少過香港?"},{"pid":"5fce87fdd1a3c29697f0172d3e5b3ceee6dbd5b2","tid":2411953,"uid":60129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">軍方又向多位著名演員、導演和歌手發出拘捕令，指控他們利用人氣和名望，去煽動民眾參加反對軍方的公民抗命運動。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c3e40f212342f249b06c0a9b7a296939a3f014","tid":2411953,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2be40b02330049d4eb369a927d2fb4d5772c5fa","tid":2411953,"uid":13221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"星期三唔洗返工咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"緬甸無乜黎生？"},{"pid":"52c3bee76db85d5c714a90b243f5ca7b363fdc47","tid":2411953,"uid":68903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:17:48.000Z","msg":"佢地遊行學香港加年華化，結果唔駛講啦"},{"pid":"35e7dee7ea93deac15f8401ca0f984f074df424e","tid":2411953,"uid":120757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcab934e27395964148b781437f15e2d810dd597","tid":2411953,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"658c5d824d6ae94489fe97bcc445b69442222fa9","tid":2411953,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"六千萬人口既國家<br />\n出黎既人仲少過香港?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"其實全世界無乜國家可以超越到香港<br />\n<br />\n700萬人口, 有200萬人上街示威<br />\n幾乎1/3人口"},{"pid":"ef73f5113d5294523568fc79b91939cad3a68cf5","tid":2411953,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"香港黑警幾時拍片支持緬甸軍方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}